Elden Ring Nightreign Ironeye Build Showcase - How I Play Ironeye
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, we're going to be giving you guys further tips on how to play Ironeye, and I'm going to do a run-through of the game as well. And kind of explain to you my decision-making process along the way, so that you can understand why I've made the decision about Ironeye in an attempt to show you how you might make better decisions about the gear that you pick up when playing Ironeye.
